                                </button>
                              </div>
                            </div>
                          </div>
                        {% else %}
                          {% comment %} 商品未找到 - 網格模式 {% endcomment %}
                          <div style="padding: 20px; text-align: center; background: rgba(255,0,0,0.1); border-radius: 8px; margin: 10px;">
                            <p>❌ {{ 'content.no_products_found' | t }}: {{ product }}</p>
